Data Sets

Auctions in a Distressed Real Estate Market in Italy

A data set with information about auctions of foreclosed properties in Italy between 2000 and 2016.

auctions_amf
Auctions in a Distressed Real Estate Market in Italy: Auction Market Features.
auctions_pf
Auctions in a Distressed Real Estate Market in Italy: Profitability Features of Property.
auctions_phy
Auctions in a Distressed Real Estate Market in Italy: Physical Features of Property.
auctions_sef
Auctions in a Distressed Real Estate Market in Italy: Socio-Economic Features.

Housing Price Gradients in Italian Capitals

A data set with information about housing price gradients in 112 provincial capitals in Italy.

price_gradient
Housing Price Gradients in Capital Cities in Italy.

Industry Readiness Index 4.0

Data related to the Industry Readiness Index 4.0 for NUTS-2 regions in Europe.

i40_index_db
Database for Industry Readiness Index 4.0.
i40_index_rank
Promethee Rankings of Industry Readiness Index 4.0.

Italian Vineyards

A sample of italian vineyards with landscape and management information.

vineyards
A sample of Italian vineyards.

Ph.D. Entrepreneurship in Italy

Data from a survey of Ph.D. students in Italy and their entrepreneurship, including spinoffs, academic institutions, and regions of Italy.

phd_italy
A qualitative survey on Ph.D. entrepreneurship in Italy.
phd_italy_regions
Regional summary of survey on Ph.D. entrepreneurship in Italy.
